Class name: ItemManager
Parent class: None
Interface: Manager

Responsibilities:
* Manage items stored in ItemStorage.
* When we call methods in ItemManager, we can do the following:
    - findName (return all items containing or relating to certain name)
    - findCategory (return all items in a specific category)
    - findOwner (return all items belong to a certain owner)
    - addItem (add item(s) to item storage)
    - removeItem (remove item(s) from item storage)
    - loadItems (     add items into storage.)

Collaborators:
- ItemStorage